{
  "stem": "10644.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A commando was-- was formed to go to work in the Port of Danzig.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are in Danzig around 10 miles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this camp?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In this camp, till the-- exactly 8th of February, '45.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the Russians came closer, and we were brought-- we went on a march.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And finally, we landed in a camp called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is near a city in-- that is Pommern.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That is a part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is a state of Germany, Pommern.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we are brought near the city, Laumberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were there for-- when we finally came-- few days-- not few days-- around two weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People from other camps joined us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And from other camps they brought typhus, paratyphus, paratyphus, typhoid, paratyphoid and typhus.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Typhus was the most dangerous thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I with my friend, Kronsoln-- there were other doctors-- they are very afraid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We went to take care of these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My dear, I, all the time, was working with the people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It is not a doctor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- I was a doctor, but I was-- therefore, you know, I-- I-- I am alive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Therefore, nobody, no one would said they've been warned about me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- I was just one of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If I didn't do it-- to be able to survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can-- so therefore, you know, whatever I can help them, I will help them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was my attitude-- truly, 100%.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you take in all the book, I give the book to [NON-ENGLISH], in a book after the war describing Riga, the [NON-ENGLISH] from Riga.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the [NON-ENGLISH] means the destruction of-- of Riga-- the-- of Riga-- of Riga Jewry-- Jewry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Germany, there is a big article about Spilve.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he, the man who wrote it, he didn't know me-- wrote, you know, on two pages about me, my behavior-- that I knew the mentality of the-- of the Germans, and even SS.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I have to talk to them, I have talked to militarily.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I answered militarily.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had military-- military education.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they liked it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --in this way, I could achieve much, much more.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so, that is the last of everything so long I was in Riga.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Riga, 30th of September, that is finished.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- I'm not a doctor anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm one of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I went, you know, to work to-- to Port of Danzig, where we order to build a railroad in the Port of Danzig.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It is a-- a branch of their railroad-- under supervision-- supervision.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had to bring, you know, only the heavy, heavy-- what goes under the--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, tight.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Here it is a metallic, trying to see your-- they use wood.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] And soaked in water, you know, how to say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's so thick, you know, under this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very heavy.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We too-- we two had to bring it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I recall, I had right away pains here on my shoulder.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my backaches now is much more worse-- worse than my other problems, the-- the things the backaches from-- from the time when I was carrying these things.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still didn't believe that I will survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got-- I was attending these-- with people with-- coming, passing by, attending-- I took a whole school-- school for these people, you know, at least to bring them into warm conditions, to give them something resembled tea, water--",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--because they were dehydrated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is already at the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is already-- already we are in the-- in the-- in the end of February, beginning of-- of-- of March-- and the beginning of March.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That how we-- that was-- and I got--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--my-- my typhus.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- when-- or an the order was to move further-- we were around 10, 12 people with typhus in a small barrack.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were maybe 20-- small barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we said, we cannot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have no-- we were sure that they-- they will come and they will kill us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Happens that just-- it came the 10th or 11th day of my sickness, the temperature comes rapidly down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you feel suddenly much better.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No medication.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had only-- I only, you know, I was getting hot water and potatoes cooked with-- with the-- with the European-- European potatoes, you have to remove the skin.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it contains-- it contains a gift called ptomaine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we-- they were cooked with the skin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We-- all right, we--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--ptomine is a poisoning.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we just now remove-- remove the skin, and we ate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] --it is-- my dear, the-- the-- here, during this night, you know, a Polish-- Polish prisoner were-- he was a-- comes running and throws us a piece of-- of horse's meat.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
